{"tid":430863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本妹不拿iPhone會被排擠　家長含淚掏錢搶舊機","createTime":"2017-10-10T07:37:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-11T14:25:38.000Z","uid":75969,"like":304,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":112,"replies":[{"pid":"23eb669b71d8b81c293bc990420bab2bbd96a8a3","tid":430863,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T07:37:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171010/640_cad5b218bc748829ad0e28e5d82c7599.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171010%2F640_cad5b218bc748829ad0e28e5d82c7599.jpg&h=52d08d8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">日本有高達6成的女子高中生都是用iPhone，甚至有學生坦承「不用iPhone就會被排擠」。翻攝網路</span><br />\n<br />\n蘋果最新一代的智慧型手機iPhone 8銷量不若以往，不過iPhone依然是日本最受歡迎的手機，根據手機小說《野草苺》於9月份的調查，日本有高達6成的女子高中生都是用iPhone，甚至有學生坦承「不用iPhone就會被排擠」，有些家長害怕子女在校被霸凌，就算買不起新機也要買二手iPhone或者型號較舊的iPhone 5。<br />\n<br />\n調查人員與數名女子高中生進行深度訪談，發現只要是iPhone就可以了，不會計較型號新舊，不過，受訪學生異口同聲說羨慕擁有新型號iPhone的女生，因為鏡頭比較好，拍出來的照片都好看一點，除此之外「有很多可愛的手機殼」、「既時尚又易用」等等，也是日本女高中生瘋iPhone的原因之一。<br />\n<br />\n另外，因為iOS跟Andriod系統的用法不同，如果身邊的朋友都用iPhone，就更容易能夠問人手機用法和推薦的應用程式，拉近與朋友的距離，「大家都在用iPhone啊，只有自己一個人不用很奇怪、會被排擠......。」（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20171010/1219526/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20171010%2F1219526%2F&d=kz8aiBPLgMO%2BSHg0%2B83J0ROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=6f7d3b3a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20171010/1219526/</a><br />\n<br />\n過嚟 等叔叔買比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf50fb2e9a03f1e63e7ddfab9b59c2f2bde2a62e","tid":430863,"uid":128014,"like":27,"dislike":200,"score":-173,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T07:40:02.000Z","msg":"有必要咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cla